Windmere Corp said it will form ajoint venture with &lt;Paragon Sales Inc>, and will be called Paragon Industries.    The equally-owned joint venture will merchandise anddistribute electric heaters, humidifiers and other electricseasonal consumer products in the U.S., according to thecompany.    The two companies, which have approximately 15 pct of theelectric fan market in the U.S., will attempt to expand thatmarket and introduce new products, Windmere said. Reuter&#3;